title: Rare Earth -  Rare Earth In Concert (1971) [FLAC]
description:
CD-reissue of the classical vinyl double-LP

Recorded live at Jacksonville, Florida Civic Coliseum, Miami Florida Marine Stadium, Ithaca, New York Cornell University and at The Pharmacy. Track 8 recorded at Motown Studios.


tracklist:

1. I Just Want to Celebrate  4:41
2. Hey Big Brother           7:26
3. Born to Wanderer          4:24
4. Get Ready                23:33
5. What'd I Say              6:29
6. Thoughts                 10:46
7. I'm Losing You           14:03
8. Nice To Be With You       2:23


lineup:


    Pete Rivera: drums, lead vocals, percussion
    Gil Bridges: woodwinds, vocals, percussion, flute
    John Persh: bass, vocals
    Ray Monette: guitars, vocals
    Mark Olson: keyboards, vocals
    Ed Guzman: conga, percussion
